## Testing Contract

- `make lint` must exit 0 with no errors
- `make repl` starts nREPL on :7888
- FlowStorm requires `(flow-storm.api/local-connect)` after `make storm`

## Boundaries

- clj-kondo runs via deps.edn alias, not system binary
- REPL binds to 127.0.0.1 only (security)
- CIDER middleware for Emacs integration

## Validation

```bash
clj -M:lint  # exits 0
```
